OL,7,FA teenage boy accused of murdering
OL,8,Fnine-year-old Aria Thorpe in Weston-
OL,9,Fsuper-Mare is set to face trial.
OL,11,FThe 15-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,12,Fbecause of his age, appeared at
OL,13,FBristol Crown Court on Friday morning.
OL,15,FDuring the brief hearing the
OL,16,Fdefendant, who appeared via video link
OL,17,Ffrom youth detention accommodation,
OL,18,Fspoke only to confirm his name.
