OL,3,CBoy, 15, accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe is set to face
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FJudge Peter Blair KC, the Recorder of
OL,8,FBristol, set a provisional trial date
OL,9,Ffor June 15 2026. The trial is
OL,10,Fexpected to last two weeks.
OL,12,FPolice were called to Lime Close in
OL,13,FWeston-super-Mare just before 6:10pm
OL,14,Fon Monday, where nine-year-old Aria
OL,15,Fhad suffered a single stab wound. The
OL,16,Fboy was arrested in nearby Worle a
OL,17,Fshort time later.
