OL,7,FAt Bristol Crown Court, the teenager
OL,8,Fwas represented by Charley Pattison,
OL,9,Fwhile Ray Tully KC appeared for the
OL,10,Fprosecution.
OL,12,FHis father was among those attending
OL,13,Fin the public gallery.
OL,15,FThe teenager is next expected to
OL,16,Fappear in court on March 16.
OL,18,FAvon and Somerset Police are
OL,19,Fcontinuing to support Aria's family,
OL,20,Fwho have requested privacy.
