OL,3,CBoy, 15, accused of murdering nine-
OL,4,Cyear-old Aria Thorpe is set to face
OL,5,Ctrial
OL,7,FSuperintendent Jen Appleford said:
OL,8,F"The tragic loss of such a young girl
OL,9,Fhas caused a huge amount of shock and
OL,10,Fupset, with there being a profound
OL,11,Fsense of loss felt throughout the
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"We are working closely with partner
OL,15,Fagencies and schools across the Weston
OL,16,Farea to make sure those affected
OL,17,Freceive access to any support they
OL,18,Fneed."
OL,20,FAria was a pupil at Becket Primary
OL,21,FSchool in Weston-super-Mare.
