OL,7,FA statement posted on their website
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our school and Trust community
OL,9,Fare devastated by the tragic death of
OL,10,Fone of our pupils, Aria Thorpe.
OL,12,F"We are working closely with
OL,13,Fprofessional agencies to ensure
OL,14,Fappropriate support is provided to our
OL,15,Fchildren, staff and families as they
OL,16,Fcome to terms with this heartbreaking
OL,17,Fnews.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts and deepest sympathies
OL,20,Fare with Aria's family during this
OL,21,Fincredibly difficult time."
